{"tid":1807704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[官宣] 寄往武漢及鄰近地區的特快專遞服務暫停","createTime":"2020-01-02T03:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T03:35:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61ec7bc82c712a3ae8bf99b626fcaea34a230766","tid":1807704,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_834.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fnotices%2Findex_id_834.html&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOADIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7d4c54e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_834.html</a><br />\n<br />\n通告<br />\n <br />\n寄往武漢及鄰近地區的特快專遞服務暫停<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019.12.24</span>(<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來24號前已開始)</span><br />\n<br />\n因受航空運輸安排影響，寄往武漢及鄰近地區(郵政編碼43XXXX至44XXXX)的特快專遞服務(經濟快遞服務除外)即時暫停，直至另行通告。"},{"pid":"dbe8ddc3e6ed5dcfbebc5856aa84f7bac045e18c","tid":1807704,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441a922fb3be3a02830b78335c5c3fc9b6e984b0","tid":1807704,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3be733726ace66ad4a0e31dd8d28ea89f9fb797","tid":1807704,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"請醫護唸方法將沙士病毒送入狗屋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}